===INGREDIENTS LIST===

FOR THE MARINADE:
1/2 cup soy sauce
2 cloves of garlic, minced
1/4 cup coconut vinegar
3/4 tbsp. sugar
1/2 tsp whole peppercorn

FOR THE SAUTE:
2 tbsp refined coconut oil
1/2 tbsp ginger, diced
2 cloves of garlic, minced
2 chili pepper, or more for extra kick (you may also save some for garnish)
1/2 yellow onion, diced
1/2 tbsp kalamansi juice, or favorite citrus like lemon or lime

FOR MAIN INGREDIENTS:
7-10 pcs Shiitake mushrooms,
diced
12 pcs Oyster mushrooms, diced
2 oz. Beech mushrooms, diced
1 block firm tofu


===FULL DETAILS OF THE GIVEAWAY===

* This giveaway is open in the U.S. and Puerto Rico only

* How to enter:

   Write a comment down below telling us your favorite tofu dish 
   and favorite characteristic of the tofu. 


* The winner gets to choose 5 out of the 8 Hodo Soy products listed on Hodo Soy's website: http://www.hodosoy.com  

- Spicy Yuba Noodles
- Sesame Yuba Noodles
- Five-Spice Tofu Nuggets
- Thai Curry Tofu Nuggets
- v-EGG-an Salad
- Firm Tofu
- Braised Tofu
- Yuba Sheets


* Hodo Soy will ship the prizes to the winning participant.  Please provide street address and phone number, NO PO Boxes accepted. Winner will be contacted directly by Hodo Soy to arrange shipping.


* This giveaway is open in the U.S. and Puerto Rico only.
